# Advanced Runtime

For multi-session or team-critical tasks:

- Keep handoffs append-only in `.cursor/handoffs/`.
- Prefer explicit status checkpoints on long tasks.
- Use deterministic checks before merge-sensitive changes.

Operational guidance:

- Treat plugin docs as source-of-truth, project `.cursor/rules/*.mdc` as runtime contract.
- Avoid broad policy copy; project should keep only required runtime rules.
